            "title": "名創優品半年經調整利升逾12%  午後股債挫逾4.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">名創優品(09896)公布，截至9月底止第三季度，經調整股東應佔利潤7.63億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年增長12.33%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內，股東應佔利潤4.41億元，按年下跌31.36%，每股盈利0.36元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖說：名創優品門店\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_CH_名創優品_source-web__-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖說：名創優品門店\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_CH_名創優品_source-web__-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖說：名創優品門店</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">收入57.97億元，按年增長28.17%，超過公司此前25%至28%指引範圍上限。毛利增長27.6%至25.9億元，毛利率則跌0.2個百分點至44.7%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">毛利率為44.7%，按年下跌0.2個百分點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">名創優品品牌的收入增加22.9%至52.2億元，其中內地收入增19.3%，於2025年逐季加速，海外收入增27.7%，收入佔比達44.3%。至於TOP TOY品牌收入增加111.4%至5.7億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">名創優品品牌的同店銷售按年錄中個位數增長，主要受惠於中國內地卓越的高個位數增長，及海外市場的低個位數增長。TOP TOY品牌的同店銷售增長提升至中個位數的增長率。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今年首9個月，經調整股東應佔利潤20.42億元，按年增長6.69%。股東應佔利潤13.47億元，按年下跌25.68%，每股盈利1.1元。收入151.9億元，按年增長23.68%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">午後股價一度跌至38.28元，跌4.92%，現跌幅收窄至1.19%，報39.7元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15444825-%e5%90%8d%e5%89%b5%e5%84%aa%e5%93%81%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%b6%93%e8%aa%bf%e6%95%b4%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be12-%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e8%82%a1%e5%82%b5%e6%8c%ab%e9%80%be4-9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240924_FI_source-web_09896-704-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-21 13:30:35",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
